track_notes: I scouted the northwest ridgeline before heading out and it looked like a Rhododendron snarl.  I do not recommend that route from the Bartram Trail.
track_title: W4G/NG-024 Rock Mtn via Bartram Trail Southbound

track_notes: The last bit of FS Road leading to Wilson Gap has gotten quite rough.  This is an alternative parking spot a short distance back up the road where the Bartram Tail crosses again.  You can either take the Bartram Trail or walk the road at this point.  Taking the road is shorter but that means it is steeper also.
track_title: W4G/NG-024 - Rock Mtn parking before ruts
